    "question_id" : 7360403,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To encrypt:</p>\n<pre><code>byte[] encrpt= text.getBytes(&quot;UTF-8&quot;);\nString base64 = Base64.encodeToString(encrpt, Base64.DEFAULT);\n</code></pre>\n<p>To decrypt:</p>\n<pre><code>byte[] decrypt= Base64.decode(base64, Base64.DEFAULT);\nString text = new String(decrypt, &quot;UTF-8&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n"
