    "body" : "<p>If you are using <strong>Kotlin</strong> than use like this</p>\n\n<p>For Encode</p>\n\n<pre><code>val password = \"Here Your String\"\nval data = password.toByteArray(charset(\"UTF-8\"))\nval base64 = Base64.encodeToString(data, Base64.DEFAULT)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>For Decode</p>\n\n<pre><code>val datasd = Base64.decode(base64, Base64.DEFAULT)\nval text = String(datasd, charset(\"UTF-8\"))\n</code></pre>\n"
